data.description: Grand two story entrance greets you and your guests as you enter the home.  The partially open concept provides an abundance of living and kitchen space with a great layout for those who like to cook and entertain. Premium 42" cabinets provide excellent storage as does the wonderful pantry.  You also have excellent counter space for food prep.  Bringing in groceries is a breeze with direct access to the kitchen from the 2 car attached garage.  There's a convenient main level 1/2 BA for guest use.   All 3 bedrooms are located on the 2nd level, as is the laundry room.  No lugging laundry up and down stairs; everything is conveniently situated near the bedrooms.  Your master suite has a generous walk-in closet, full en suite bathroom, and is separated from the other 2 bedrooms for a bit of privacy.  A 2nd full bathroom is located on the upstairs level as well.  Neighborhood has direct access to nature preserve trails. Walk or ride bikes through scenic paved paths and let the day's stress slip away.  But hurry!  Don't let this home slips away from you! NEW FLOORING just installed.  Who doesn't love that fresh, clean smell of NEW?  Kind of like buying a new car, only way better!
